{"tid":576113,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"fg第一份工捱一年係咪真係咁緊要?","createTime":"2018-02-28T15:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T14:03:03.000Z","uid":22929,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f704cb599305b3d8eb8da546d5eefb35239ce0bf","tid":576113,"uid":22929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:41:14.000Z","msg":"17fg 係間大公司做左半年 <br />\n我直屬呀頭早我少少入間公司 初初除左話OT多同辛苦都無咩太大怨言<br />\n但自從近呢兩個月條友過左probation之後 開始係咁乜都叫人幫佢做 射哂d野俾我同幾個同級同事 甚至有d係over左我地duty既野都照係咁 <br />\n依家愈做愈唔開心 個腦成日都諗幾時辭職<br />\n搵身邊朋友屋企人傾佢地都係叫我反正都做左半年捱多陣 搞到個人好迷惘到底係咪真係留係到多幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  岩岩開頭一份工既一年經驗到底係咪真係咁重要?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560a611221769b6ae2504a9fe06d58382073dcbc","tid":576113,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:43:37.000Z","msg":"之後做返呢行定點？"},{"pid":"c1485874f57e378dd103deeeb522340971cd580a","tid":576113,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"038d91d0db4cc6f2ba39c8fa00149ff3761df284","tid":576113,"uid":164532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c1485874f57e378dd103deeeb522340971cd580a","tid":576113,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"唔係"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:46:49.000Z","msg":"咩類型工作？<br />\n<br />\n如果將來未必做尼行，不如邊搵新邊做住先"},{"pid":"7c9d91eb6421737dfb0308cc44beab14fece5b16","tid":576113,"uid":172810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"其實就算做夠一年嘅exp都唔係啲咩嘢<br />\n不過呢啲人基本上間間公司都有"},{"pid":"5c57232e4bd53a37eb08fe0c668ce4177cd0dbbc","tid":576113,"uid":164532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c9d91eb6421737dfb0308cc44beab14fece5b16","tid":576113,"uid":172810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"其實就算做夠一年嘅exp都唔係啲咩嘢<br />\n不過呢啲人基本上間間公司都有"}